Franchising
 
The art of growing your business from A to Z.   


60 YEARS OF EXPERIENCE. Diversified Franchise Group (DFG), a Delaware corporation, is a franchise development company. DFG acquires early to mid-stage underperforming franchisors (50 – 100 units) and emerging franchisors (unique franchise concepts that have not been developed or have little competition).  Read about our team  here.










Process
 







Process
 



THE PROBLEM







The founders of Diversified Franchise Group developed this concept because it was clear that franchise consultants and the investment community were not providing what emerging franchising companies really need - capital AND manpower support. DFG provides both. THE SOLUTIONInstead of investing passively in a franchiseable business, the Company will create a development arrangement between Diversified Franchise Group and the company that wishes to franchise its business. DFG will organize an operating company (the “Franchise Company”) for the sole purpose of developing the franchise and will be a wholly owned subsidiary of Diversified Franchise Group. The Company provides funding to the new entity and all the manpower required to develop and build a national franchise network.  










































