Company Summary





Diversified Franchise Group (DFG), is a franchise development company. The Company will acquire early to mid-stage underperforming franchisors (50 – 100 units) and emerging franchisors (unique franchise concepts that have not been developed or have little competition).  DFG draws upon the 37 years of franchise  experience of its founder, Brian Pappas and the 30+ years of franchise experience of his brother Jeff.  










